But I swear to god, it hurts every second. And I know I’m a bit anatomically lopsided, but does one of my ribs look swollen?

I’m not trying to be a hypochondriac, but I feel like I was just brushed aside.

It’s just frustrating he refused to x-ray me or anything. No pain meds, nothing. I just lay here hoping breathing gets easier soon.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QcFXPzG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[snakevenominablackdress]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>SPOT ON</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IlWrOrZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Gzf9xBW.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IlWrOrZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sosickofthisshit]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Marley the painting penguin</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aKs2C1c</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tELvZ3l.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Moody Gardens, Galveston TX</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aKs2C1c</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ozzy890]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Breaking Cirno</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2VwqVhm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YA4zAI8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2VwqVhm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MatyasV]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We never stood a chance</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XAMD3Hw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Dry8KBu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mKO6iDG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N8SJkYP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/s20P7yH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TKNgvUK.jpg" s