ged on a hobby I genuinely enjoyed because of the way I look. I can't control how the fact I'm a large burly man. Every woman I talk to about it in person just treats me like I'm a creep, every guy treats me like I'm a pussy. After work I'm packing my sewing equipment away. No more tailoring, no more dresses, no more cosplay, no more adding pockets to shit. No more. 

If anyone asks my hobbies are weightlifting, deiting, and screaming into the void.

Edit: I gave away the dresses I made. I did this for skill and to make the world a prettier place, not internet points and clearly not to get laid. All I have left is my very shitty first attempt at making a suit that I kept as a reminder of how far I'd come. Not far enough apparently.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IRNA93T</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Beattywill80]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ukrainian soldier, enjoying a coffee while artillery lands close by but it doesn't dampen his mood</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0a9C2gX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nCM7Kva.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0a9C2gX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Combatant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cute animals are cute</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Lulb6sj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3WiSI62.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iWnfziE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Wu46ts5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GMtCjNl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GNVlOOl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9Vg4b6p.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XqT37hS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GUjiSnt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TTjPFV9.jpg" style="max-wid